TY  - JOUR
TI  - Resource Allocation Under Asymmetric Information
AU  - Harris, Milton
AU  - Townsend, Robert M.
AB  - [The purpose of this paper is to provide a method for characterizing efficient allocation processes and efficient allocations for a large class of environments in which asymmetric information is an important factor. This method is based on a rigorous application of statistical decision theory and makes explicit both the information available to agents ex ante and the way in which information is transmitted during any multistage allocation process.]
C1  - Full publication date: Jan., 1981
DB  - JSTOR
DO  - 10.2307/1911125
