TY  - JOUR
TI  - Criteres Simples pour la Prise en Compte du Risque
AU  - Henry, Claude
AB  - [This paper deals with rules suitable for evaluating risky consequences of economic projects when various forms of stochastic dependence have to be taken into account. The Validity of various certainty-equivalence results, including the Arrow-Lind theorem, are reexamined in this framework.]
